data.description: Your Friendly Neighborhood Bald Guy proudly presents 'The Lux of Valencia Lakes'! This abode offers a spacious 2,419 square feet of relaxation! As you enter, you'll be welcomed with the mighty coffered ceilings beautifully designed to catch your attention! All three bedrooms are split with their own space across the home with an additional office/den to use as you please! The owner's suite boasts TWO walk-in closets and a bathroom which houses both a tub and a shower! Do you have an abundance of guests? This is a home with room to entertain them; There are TWO great rooms: the living room is combined with the kitchen and dinette while the family room is combined with the dining room! Of course, you'd be astounded by the granite countertops in the kitchen and the gorgeous bay windows in the dinette, however, if you turned your gaze toward the overly sized 3 panel sliding glass doors, you'd be tempted to walk into the screened-in lanai which has a serene view of the pond! This heavenly abode offers both a water softener and a water filtration system for the entirety of the home! Keep cool in the summer's heat with a completely NEW HVAC system and upgraded window blinds! Admire the beauty of the painter's touch: Full exterior, trim, garage door, and front door newly painted! Looking for some recreation or entertainment? There's no need to leave Valencia since the 'Lakes' offers so much: Entertainment Center, Bistro, pools, card rooms, fitness center, art center, Clubs, Educational Seminars, Tennis courts, Bocce ball courts, and Pickle Ball courts. Ride your golf cart around for the scenic view of the many beautiful ponds and lakes that Valencia has to offer! The HOA fee includes the membership for the clubhouse, Cable TV, high-speed internet, security monitoring system, and lawn maintenance/irrigation. Valencia Lakes is a top-rated 55+ community! Reach out to Your Friendly Neighborhood Bald Guy to schedule your private showing of 'The Lux of Valencia Lakes'!
